they said it was a novel idea but no loan company would give 
a person a loan to build with something so unconventional he 
said 
earlier this year scherbak confronted a real and present 
problem roaches under the kitchen sink 
commercial roach traps didnt work he said sprays were toxic 
and he didnt want to endanger his familys health 
so he began mixing common household ingredients until he found 
a nontoxic combination that worked he wont say whats in it 
because its not patented yet 
he put it in a spray can labeled zez the worlds first 
nontoxic roach spray 
he carries the can along with a plastic gallon jug full of live 
roaches and a large metal kettle for demonstrations 
after dumping four roaches into the kettle he sprayed them with 
zez as they died he sprayed the product into his eyes and mouth 
the roaches are dead but im ok he said 
hes not bashful in attempts to market the stuff 
last month he wrote to the entertainment director of the 
tonight show saying hed like to meet nebraska native johnny 
carson and demonstrate his product on the television show 
theres still no word from hollywood but at least we dont 
have roaches under our sink anymore he said 
