in renfrew ontario as security 
pawlowski was arrested monday in renfrew about 60 miles west of 
ottawa and charged with eight counts of murder four under 
criminal code provisions dealing with war crimes and four with 
crimes against humanity 
he is accused of murdering 410 jews and 80 nonjewish poles in 
1942 in the byelorussian republic of the soviet union 400 jews in 
the small village of snov 10 more who escaped the first killings 
