<TEXT>
diana vreeland flamboyant arbiter of the fashion world who 
edited two leading womens magazines and coined the phrase the 
beautiful people exact age unknown but believed to be about 86 
irving stone whose biographical novels of vincent van gogh 
michelangelo and sigmund freud brought history to life for millions 
of readers age 86 
joseph alsop longtime political columnist age 78 
</TEXT>
