continue from time to time regarding mutually acceptable methods 
for improving the trusts financial flexibility and enhancing value 
for all shareholders the sec filing said 
in october manville a forest products and construction 
materials concern offered to purchase about 500 million of its 
preferred stock from the trust at market prices on dec 7 
