software that will allow companies using officevision to exchange 
computer documents and electronic mail with office systems made by 
digital equipment corp wang laboratories inc hewlettpackard 
co and others ibm said 
officevision introduced by ibm in may allows companies using 
various ibm computers of different sizes to tie them together in 
one system the software overcomes the incompatibility of many ibm 
products a shortfall that has been exploited by digital and other 
companies that make only compatible machines 
the softswitch products will be sold by both ibm and 
softswitch they will be available dec 29 and will be priced from 
40000 to 250000 ibm said 
